<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 shì shéi zài hēi yè bǎ dēng diǎn liàng, shì shéi yī zhí zhàn zài shǒu wàng lóu shàng.
 shì shéi fān yuè nà wú rén fān yuè de shān gǎng, shì shéi chù chù zài xún zhǎo mí yáng.
 shì shén de hǎo zhōng pū mò mò qú láo de rén. tā men bù zhēng jìng yě bù xuān rǎng.
 xiàng yī duǒ bǎi hé huā zài huāng jiāo zhōng qiāo rán kāi fàng, shén zǎo yǐ yuè nà de xīn xiāng.
 fú shì zhǔ de rén yǒu qiān qiān wàn wàn, shéi zhēn xīn ài zhǔ, zhǔ dōu jì zài xīn shàng.
 cǐ shí wèn wèn zì jǐ zhàn zài hé fāng, cǐ shí wèn wèn zì jǐ zhàn zài hé fāng.</lyrics>
<title>shì shéi 迦南1177</title>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>1177</hymn_number>
</song>